    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for natural courses of water flowing continuously along a defined bed on the surface of the earth, forming a river, rivulet, brook, etc. The term is not used for canals or other artificial watercourses.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
